data.description: What an amazing opportunity to own a home near the Seminole area. Remarkable home with brick elevation and bay windows. Nice and bright, with a great floorplan.  This move-in ready ranch house with three spacious bedrooms is ready for it's new owner.  Carpet and a couple newer coats of paint inside several years ago and a nicer flat-top glass range and freezer on bottom refrigerator. The house is accented with nice wooden finishing's, has been updated since its construction in most respects, including siding, soffit, screens, kitchen, and bathroom. The detached workshop has full power ran to it; perfect for the handyman or to set up for sporting events. Very large master bedroom and a second bath could be installed where the laundry room is.
